        self.head = None

    # Function to insert new node at the end

        if not self.head:
            self.head = Node(data)
        else:
            current = self.head  
            while current.next:
                current = current.next  
            current.next = Node(data)  

    # Print the linked list 
    def print_list(self):
        current = self.head  
        while current:
            print(current.data, end=" ")
            current = current.next  
        print()

    # Function to reverse the linked list 
    def reverse(self): 
        prev = None  
        current = self.head  
        while current:  
            next_node = current.next  
            current.next = prev  
            prev = current  
            current = next_node  
        self.head = prev
